wdi-BN.GSR.MRCH.CD.def: Net trade in goods is the difference between exports and imports of goods. Trade in services is not included. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BN.GSR.MRCH.CD.name: Net trade in goods
wdi-BN.GSR.MRCH.CD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
